                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9140" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2288</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3007 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大国重器：陕汽控股数字化转型中的管理模式变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Big Country Heavy Duty: Management Model Reforms during the Digital Transformation of Shaanqi Holdings</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江旭，邱洱琦，董雪艳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西汽车控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕汽控股；数字化转型；管理模式变革；数字化组织；2024百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shaanqi holdings; digital transformation; management mode transformation; digital organization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西汽车控股集团有限公司（陕汽控股）是中国西部重型军用车辆与大型全系列商用车辆制造龙头企业，致力于汽车整车及零部件的研发、生产和销售。为了解决传统生产模式下劳动密集度高、生产效率低的难题，陕汽控股推行了数字化转型，并实现了数字化系统的全面应用，助推了企业在国内国外市场的“双赢”。然而，数字化转型也带来了新的挑战，如何利用数字技术实现企业管理模式的蜕变与跃迁，推动企业数字化组织和全球战略的协同发展，是陕汽控股持续思考的问题。本案例详细描述了陕汽控股如何通过不断深化数字化转型，构建覆盖全产业链的数字生态体系，并借助精准智能的数字化管理决策手段，助推多产业融通发展的管理模式变革历程。本案例旨在为相关专业的学生提供深入学习和理解数字时代企业管理模式变革方法及过程的机会。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Shaanxi Automobile Holding Group Co., Ltd. (Shaanqi) is a large state-owned automobile manufacturing enterprise in western China, specializing in the research, development, production and sales of automobiles and parts. To address issues concerning high labor intensity and low productivity in traditional production modes, Shaanqi has undergone a digital transformation, implementing digital systems that enable quick and efficient managerial decision-making. This has facilitated Shaanqi’s entry into the international arena and has created a &quot;win-win&quot; situation in both the domestic and international markets. However, digital transformation has also brought new challenges. One of the key ongoing issues for Shaanxi Automobile Holdings is how to leverage digital technology to transform and leapfrog the entire lifecycle management model, and to promote the synergistic development of the digital organization and global strategy. This case study describes how Shaanqi continues to deepen its digital transformation, builds a digital ecosystem for the entire industry chain, adopts more accurate and intelligent digital management decisions to boost the development of multi-industry integration, and helps students of related majors to learn and understand the methods and processes of the change of enterprise management mode in the digital era.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理学》、《战略管理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Burke-Litwin变革模型；工程变更7R原则；Kotter 8步变革模型；ADKAR变更管理模型；麦肯锡7S模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
